text: Jyada likh dunga to tu visibility no kr dega. Isliye nhi likhunga kyuki aise bhi tujhe to sab jante hi hai. But ek bat hai yar tu ab dedicated hogya hai
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text:
Sale aman gautam. sorry bhai aise start krne ke liye. Lekin bhai ek chij jo tmne proof kr di hai ki hardwork krne se kuch bhi possible ho skta hai. You are rocking man. Aise hi hardwork se duniya hila dena bro. Thnks for being part in IITk. 
Milte hai in future
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text: Pandey yar tm mera sach mai accha wala bhai tha. Jo bhi prblm hoti thi tu always help kr deta tha. Chahe emotional ho ya financial problem. Hmlog to aise bhi first day bhi sath the collge ke aur last day bhi sath the. One of the best person in my college life. Aur chapu to tu hai him aise hi chahpte rehna hmeshaa
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text:
Sach mai yar hmara jyada interaction to nhi hua but jitta hua bhut sahi tha. 
Ek course mai the same but lgta hi nhi tha. Aisa lgta tha ki mai tmhe kbse janta hu. Hmesha aise hi rehna bro. Bhul mt jana. Ek bat aur bhut confident bnde ho yar tm.

Haan yar thnks for soc479.

Take care. Be safe milenge bro in future pakka...
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text: Kya likhu samjh nhi aata. But may be sbse jyada collge ka tym sayad tmhare sath hi spend kiya hoga. Sayad ek do course chodkr sare oe, sare de and almost sare hss bhi same. text:
Ip sayad hmlog to first day hi mil liye the. But ip yar jitta tmne group project mai mehnat ki utta sayad kre. Sara kam tm aur Ashutosh kr lete the. Mai fraud na hokr bhi fraud bn jana padta tha. Almost civil ke sare labs mai sath the. Thnks for being in my college life ip. Intern ke tym tmne bhut madad ki thi yar. Mera bhi kam kr dete the group mai.

Bs ek hi bat khlti hai kabhi apne love life ke bare mai tmne nhi btaya.

text:

text:
Bhai, jannta to tmhe first year se hi hu. But mainly hamari dosti Ce766A ke wajh se jyada badh gayi. Project ke liye mai har jgh tmhe bol deta tha room, mess ya corridor ki aaj krte hai tm bolte the aj kr lenge but kiye at the last moment but jo bhi kiye phad diye. 
Jo bhii ho mst bnde ho yar tm kuldeep. Have a bright future kuldeep.....
Bhul mt jana foreign jane ke bad.
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text:
Bhai kya likhu tmhare bare mai. You are one of the best person that i met in IITK. Sach mai yar tu dil ka bhut accha hai. E last ke 2 mahine to sbse jyada tere sath hi bitaye hai. Bhut yad aayenge wo last ke din yar. Wo dhadkan song wo pitch experiment wo cricket wo wing cricket yar sb yad aayengee.

Abhi bhi bhut miss kr raha hu bhai. Jldi milte hai bhai. Be in touch naveen
author: Abhishek  Gupta

text:
Aur mittal kaise ho bhai? 
First of all yar tm chapu to ho hi, isme na koi shak hai na koi doubt. IITK mai sbse phle to tmse hi mila. Mere one of the best bhai. 
Bs ek bat rah gayi yar last tym mai mil lete to bhut accha rehta yar. Bhai aajate campus ek bar mil lete. Koi na future mai milenge. And yar tu sach mai bhut helpful hai. And onething agr in future jarurat pade to pakka help krna.
Last But not tu hai chota but dhamka bada krta hai.
Agr mere se kabhi glti hui ho to maf kr dena.
Miss you broo too much. Milte hai in future kabhi bhiii.
author: Abhishek  Gupta
